    "longBusinessSummary": "Refrigeration Electrical Engineering Corporation, together with its subsidiaries, produces, transmits, and distributes renewable electricity using hydro, solar, and wind power in Vietnam. The company operates through Mechanical and Refrigeration Electrical Engineering; Real Estate and Office Leasing; Power; and Water segments. The company operates as a mechanical and electrical engineering contractor, which provides consulting, design, procurement, installation, testing and commissioning, and maintenance services for the commercial, residential, industrial and infrastructure sectors; and as an EPC contractor for commercial and industrial rooftop solar projects. It also offers air ducts, air dampers, air diffusers, air conditioners, and trunking products under the Reetech brand name; and water supply, treatment, and distribution services. In addition, the company develops and manages real estate; and leases and manages office buildings. Further, it engages in trading and electricity trading; service supply; digital services; and strategic financial investments in the infrastructure related sector. Refrigeration Electrical Engineering Corporation was founded in 1977 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
